Name: HyperCard

Synonyms: hypertalk, hc, hypercard, xTalk

Type: glossary

Description:
The defunct authoring environment from Apple Computer (1987 - 2004) that was the
main progenitor of all xTalk scripting environments. Its scripting language was
called HyperTalk, and third party clones of that scripting language, such as
SuperTalk, MediaTalk, MetaTalk, etc., collectively became known to the public as
xTalk.
